	  <div class="itemExtraFields">
		<div> 
		<h2><a href='/author/itemlist/user/49346'>Fania Davis</a></h2>
<div><p>Fania Davis is co-founder and executive director of Restorative Justice for Oakland Youth. She practiced civil rights law for 27 years. Her Ph.D. in indigenous studies led to her work in restorative justice.</p></div> 
		</div> 	
